data.description: Riviera @ Freehold a Toll Brothers Built Gated Community is now offering a Tradition Manor situated on a cul da sac lot. This home sits on one of the largest premium lots and has complete backyard privacy backing to woods. It has custom paver sidewalk in the front and patio in the rear. The interior has an open floor plan with 10ft ceilings, custom moldings, tray ceilings and large walk in closet in the Master BDRM. The F/R has a gas fireplace and the kitchen is upgraded with granite tops.
